    67	 * would be a builder creation candidate. Then the return type of {@code Person#builder}, {@code Builder}, is
    68	 * investigated for a parameterless method that returns {@code Person}. When {@code Builder#create} is found
    69	 * the {@link BuilderInfo} is created with the {@code Person#builder} as a builder creation method and
    70	 * {@code Builder#create} as a build method.
