   142	     * {@link DefaultBuilderProvider#isPossibleBuilderCreationMethod(ExecutableElement, TypeElement)} and
   143	     * {@link DefaultBuilderProvider#findBuildMethods(TypeElement, TypeElement)} to create the
   144	     * {@link BuilderInfo}.
   145	     * <p>
   146	     * The default implementation uses {@link DefaultBuilderProvider#shouldIgnore(TypeElement)} to check if the
   147	     * {@code typeElement} should be ignored.
   148	     * <p>
