   222	     * build method for {@code typeElement}.
   223	     * <p>
   224	     * The default implementation uses {@link DefaultBuilderProvider#shouldIgnore(TypeElement)} to check if the
   225	     * {@code builderElement} should be ignored, i.e. not checked for build elements.
   226	     * <p>
   227	     * If there are multiple methods that satisfy
   228	     * {@link DefaultBuilderProvider#isBuildMethod(ExecutableElement, TypeElement)} and one of those methods
   229	     * is names {@code build} that that method would be considered as a build method.
   230	     * @param builderElement the element for the builder
   231	     * @param typeElement the element for the type that is being built
   232	     * @return the build method for the {@code typeElement} if it exists, or {@code null} if it does not
